{
  "stem": "26609.16",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] She didn't want to tell me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Later, much later, she told me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "She didn't talk of Nazis at all, only said they are good people.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "That's what happened to me there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And the day-- [PAUSES FOR 2 SECONDS] only at nighttime in my room, I cried, because I didn't know what happened to my child.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Partly I knew what happened to my family.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I knew before.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I knew how my sister gave herself up with a little child.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Only don't know what happened to her, and how they killed her, and how that little child, the little boy of five, her first child-- I know nothing.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And I don't know what-- I know what happened because a person who survived when I was years later from Australia, from here, to Germany-- to Israel, I met someone whom I knew before the war from Grodek, where my parents died.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "He told me only that he knew how they marched them all to a forest where they were all killed.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "But I don't know if my mother and father ever reached that forest.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "If they didn't fell-- and I'm quite sure-- but I don't know.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "No one told me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] So I'm sure that they fell before and other people walked over them.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And the Gestapo didn't allow anyone to help anyone if they fell.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Because for weeks, they didn't eat anything.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And my mother wasn't a very strong person, neither my father.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "They were not like other people.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 2 SECONDS] They were slim and tall.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And my mother survived.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And my little brother of 13 was beaten so long until-- and he screamed, mama.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "He thought mama can help him.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
